00:30:58.058 --> 00:30:59.600
so you have to marry someone

00:30:59.600 --> 00:31:01.250
who speaks a different language from you,

00:31:01.250 --> 00:31:03.690
that creates a marriage bond
between other communities,

00:31:03.690 --> 00:31:05.193
there's also communal rituals.

00:31:06.785 --> 00:31:08.035
